Puppet module: users

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages NameMedia's users and groups
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include users              # Install and run users with standard configurations.
include users::disable     # Disable users service.
include users::disableboot # Disable users service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include users::absent      # Remove users package.

DEPENDENCIES:
